short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Listen Friday Night Funkin' songs directly in your tab. Play FNF music and find your favorite soundtrack.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Listen to the original soundtrack and songs from Friday Night Funkin' and start dancing, working, learning, or anything you like.

The songs are made by Isaac Garcia, known as Kawai Sprite. All the rights reserved by Kawai Sprite. The images from the extension are own by ninjamuffin99 and his team that worked on this open source game project.

The [FNF] Friday Night Funkin' Songs extensions is made by fans of the Friday Night Funkin game for all the fans. If this extension is violating any rights, please inform us.

Click your favorite song and start listen it. After it start, you can move to other tabs and your music will play without interruption.

Updates:

[14.05.2021] New FNF songs are added, including Bopeebo, Fresh, High, Breakfast or Satin Panties.
